description:
Moon - Central America (2016).epub Gooner

Publisher: Avalon Travel Publishing (2 Feb. 2016)
Language: English
ISBN: 9781631214165

An ebook exclusive, Moon Central America combines Moon's full-length guides to seven Central American countries into one comprehensive digital guide.

Moon Central America includes the following country guides:

Moon Belize
Moon Costa Rica
Moon El Salvador
Moon Guatemala
Moon Honduras & the Bay Islands
Moon Nicaragua
Moon Panama

For each country, you'll find trustworthy advice from Moon's experienced travel authors. Professional photographer Al Argueta compiles the best places to take in Guatemala's awe-inspiring volcanoes, and adventure traveler Amy Robertson shares her list of Honduras's best places to get face-to-face with natureâ€”from caves to cloud forests.

If you're dreaming of a Central American trip of any length or mix of destinations, Moon Central America is the travel companion for you
